# Community + Drizzle

- Schema and migrations live under `community/src/migrations/`; align with `community/drizzle.config.ts`.
- Keep migration files small and reversible where possible; follow existing naming (`v001_*`, etc.).
- Use Drizzle patterns already present in the package; do not introduce a second ORM layer.
